{"tha-ap243:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap243:0.2":"Tuvaradayakavagga ","tha-ap243:0.3":"1 Tuvaradayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap243:1.1":"“Migaluddo pure asim, ","tha-ap243:1.2":"aranne kanane aham; ","tha-ap243:1.3":"Bharitva tuvaramadaya, ","tha-ap243:1.4":"sanghassa adadim aham. ","tha-ap243:2.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap243:2.2":"yam danamadadim tada; ","tha-ap243:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap243:2.4":"tuvarassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap243:3.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap243:3.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap243:3.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap243:3.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap243:4.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma tuvaradayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap243:5.1":"Tuvaradayakattherassapadanam pathamam. "}